is not that scary.

41
00:02:39,493 --> 00:02:41,413
I want to take this opportunity

42
00:02:41,493 --> 00:02:42,653
to see if he's the type

43
00:02:42,733 --> 00:02:43,933
who gets tougher

44
00:02:44,013 --> 00:02:45,292
with setbacks

45
00:02:45,372 --> 00:02:47,013
and be responsible for the family.

46
00:02:47,252 --> 00:02:48,493
After what I've been through,

47
00:02:48,573 --> 00:02:49,254
let me tell you,

48
00:02:49,334 --> 00:02:51,612
I've learned from experience

49
00:02:51,692 --> 00:02:52,733
and grown wiser.

50
00:02:53,532 --> 00:02:54,653
No wise man

51
00:02:54,733 --> 00:02:55,972
would say they are wise.

52
00:02:57,333 --> 00:02:59,372
At your college reunion today,

53
00:02:59,733 --> 00:03:00,732
did you meet

54
00:03:00,812 --> 00:03:02,412
anyone you didn't want to see?

55
00:03:03,092 --> 00:03:04,532
I did.

56
00:03:05,652 --> 00:03:06,892
Hu Xiaojiao came to me,

57
00:03:06,972 --> 00:03:08,933
saying to give Qian Hao back to me,

58
00:03:09,013 --> 00:03:10,972
so we can have a family reunion.

59
00:03:31,972 --> 00:03:33,733
Qian Hao, are you insane?

60
00:03:34,053 --> 00:03:34,934
Sitting there

61
00:03:35,014 --> 00:03:36,053
without making a sound.

62
00:03:36,293 --> 00:03:37,613
Xu Kaixin

63
00:03:37,773 --> 00:03:38,732
bothered me,

64
00:03:38,812 --> 00:03:40,093
and you scared me.

65
00:03:40,173 --> 00:03:40,852
If you want me to

66
00:03:40,932 --> 00:03:41,533
move out,

67
00:03:41,613 --> 00:03:42,374
just say it.

68
00:03:42,454 --> 00:03:43,733
