What I said before was all out of anger.

89
00:05:35,373 --> 00:05:36,373
I'm sorry.

90
00:05:38,052 --> 00:05:39,052
I was wrong.

91
00:05:40,013 --> 00:05:41,253
Every prenatal check-up,

92
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:42,373
I'll go with you.

93
00:05:44,013 --> 00:05:45,013
I will treat him

94
00:05:45,453 --> 00:05:46,532
and raise him

95
00:05:46,612 --> 00:05:47,732
