Please

101
00:06:05,333 --> 00:06:06,972
don't leave me.

102
00:06:13,573 --> 00:06:14,573
Calm down.

103
00:06:16,532 --> 00:06:17,813
Okay, I'm with you.

104
00:06:18,333 --> 00:06:19,573
I'm with you.

105
00:06:21,013 --> 00:06:22,333
Calm down.

106
00:06:23,492 --> 00:06:24,773
Okay, I'm with you.

107
00:06:27,532 --> 00:06:29,573
No one is pitiful without cause.

108
00:06:29,773 --> 00:06:31,572
Look at Qian Hao's family,

109
00:06:31,652 --> 00:06:33,133
turning good days into this.

110
00:06:33,213 --> 00:06:34,253
Who to blame?

111
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:36,253
They reap what they sow.

112
00:06:36,333 --> 00:06:36,854
Exactly.

113
00:06:36,934 --> 00:06:38,773
People shouldn't do evil.

114
00:06:40,092 --> 00:06:42,173
By the way, Qian Hao called me,

115
00:06:42,253 --> 00:06:44,012
saying his mom misses
the two grandchildren

116
00:06:44,092 --> 00:06:45,172
so much,

117
00:06:45,453 --> 00:06:47,532
and asked me to bring the kids over
on the weekend.

118
00:06:47,612 --> 00:06:48,374
Anyway,

119
00:06:48,454 --> 00:06:50,212
they have paid me child support,

120
00:06:50,292 --> 00:06:51,292
so I agreed.

121
00:06:51,573 --> 00:06:52,573
Two grandchildren?

122
00:06:52,813 --> 00:06:55,652
I think she just wants
to see her grandson.

123
00:06:55,732 --> 00:06:56,453
I can't

124
00:06:56,533 --> 00:06:57,853
let Xiaomi go alone.

125
00:06:57,933 --> 00:06:59,612
Dami would be upset if she found out.

126
00:07:00,213 --> 00:07:01,333
When they got there,

127
00:07:01,492 --> 00:07:03,253
if she and Qian Hao were biased,

128
00:07:03,333 --> 00:07:04,452
Dami would feel worse.

129
00:07:04,532 --> 00:07:05,572
Listen, I am

130
00:07:05,652 --> 00:07:06,732
quite clever.

131
00:07:06,933 --> 00:07:07,972
Guess what?

132
00:07:08,052 --> 00:07:10,012
I made Qian Hao transfer 8,000 yuan

133
00:07:10,092 --> 00:07:11,773
to me as a deposit.

134
00:07:12,133 --> 00:07:13,332
If Dami

135
00:07:13,412 --> 00:07:14,532
comes back happily,

136
00:07:14,612 --> 00:07:16,092
I'll refund the money to him.

137
00:07:16,172 --> 00:07:17,133
If Dami

138
00:07:17,213 --> 00:07:18,733
suffers any grievance,

139
00:07:18,813 --> 00:07:19,813
I'll take the money

140
00:07:19,893 --> 00:07:21,773
for Dami as her dowry.

141
00:07:21,933 --> 00:07:23,933
You make Dami like a money grubber.

142
00:07:24,052 --> 00:07:25,933
As if she's not.

143
00:07:26,412 --> 00:07:27,412
That's true.

144
00:07:27,652 --> 00:07:30,052
She is good at everything,

145
00:07:30,453 --> 00:07:31,613
but on these matters,

146
00:07:31,693 --> 00:07:32,693
she is quite sensitive,

147
00:07:32,813 --> 00:07:34,373
much better than her mom.

148
00:07:34,453 --> 00:07:35,213
In the future,

149
00:07:35,293 --> 00:07:36,572
no one could fool her.

150
00:07:36,652 --> 00:07:38,373
Why involved me?

151
00:07:47,092 --> 00:07:48,092
Master.

152
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:50,373
Are you married?

153
00:07:52,693 --> 00:07:54,013
When I was young...

154
00:07:55,292 --> 00:07:56,292
No.

155
00:07:57,453 --> 00:07:58,453
Once,

156
00:07:58,852 --> 00:08:00,333
a girl loved me so much.

157
00:08:01,292 --> 00:08:02,292
She was beautiful

158
00:08:02,652 --> 00:08:03,652
and kind.

159
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:06,492
Once?

160
00:08:07,172 --> 00:08:08,373
Then it didn't end well.

161
00:08:09,453 --> 00:08:10,453
Got dumped?

162
00:08:11,292 --> 00:08:13,292
Do you look down on me?

163
00:08:14,333 --> 00:08:16,573
Indeed, I am not handsome,

164
00:08:16,732 --> 00:08:18,292
but I am quite manly.

165
00:08:18,813 --> 00:08:20,172
Back when I was young,

166
00:08:20,333 --> 00:08:22,013
many girl fell for me

167
00:08:22,292 --> 00:08:23,693
and tried to

168
00:08:23,773 --> 00:08:25,212
pursue me.

169
00:08:25,292 --> 00:08:26,492
I had to reject them all.

170
00:08:27,732 --> 00:08:29,933
I'm so impressed, Master.

171
00:08:30,013 --> 00:08:31,013
Right?

172
00:08:35,293 --> 00:08:38,173
Until I met her,

173
00:08:38,813 --> 00:08:39,813
I finally understood

174
00:08:40,693 --> 00:08:41,933
that love

175
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:45,092
is not that ordinary.

176
00:08:46,293 --> 00:08:47,333
If she really stands

177
00:08:47,413 --> 00:08:48,413
in front of you

178
00:08:48,813 --> 00:08:49,892
and gives you a smile,

179
00:08:51,732 --> 00:08:52,374
you would

180
00:08:52,454 --> 00:08:53,972
want to give her the whole world.

181
00:08:56,413 --> 00:08:57,413
Since you loved her,

182
00:08:57,892 --> 00:08:59,492
why did you two break up?

183
00:09:01,132 --> 00:09:02,693
Because you didn't have money?

184
00:09:03,612 --> 00:09:05,933
Did she hate your job at the cemetery?

185
00:09:07,092 --> 00:09:08,133
No, no.

186
00:09:08,213 --> 00:09:09,333
I don't deserve her.

187
00:09:11,492 --> 00:09:12,772
But it's pretty good now.

188
00:09:13,693 --> 00:09:14,772
She got married

189
00:09:15,413 --> 00:09:16,573
and has kids.

190
00:09:17,333 --> 00:09:18,612
She's living quite a good life.

191
00:09:19,533 --> 00:09:20,533
It's quite nice.

192
00:09:24,533 --> 00:09:26,772
Alright, let's call it a day.

193
00:09:28,533 --> 00:09:29,173
Tonight,

194
00:09:29,253 --> 00:09:31,412
I'll set up a camp bed

195
00:09:31,492 --> 00:09:32,333
in the office

196
00:09:32,413 --> 00:09:33,453
and keep you accompany

197
00:09:33,533 --> 00:09:34,533
for two more days.

198
00:09:35,173 --> 00:09:37,173
By the way,
if you need anything at night,

199
00:09:37,693 --> 00:09:38,692
don't knock on the door.

200
00:09:38,772 --> 00:09:39,413
Here,

201
00:09:39,493 --> 00:09:41,333
knocking on the door
can scare me to death.

202
00:09:42,252 --> 00:09:42,932
Just call.

203
00:09:43,012 --> 00:09:44,012
Okay?

204
00:09:45,053 --> 00:09:46,453
You've been here for 20 years,

205
00:09:46,533 --> 00:09:47,573
and you're still scared?

206
00:09:49,892 --> 00:09:51,132
Of course.

207
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:52,333
If I wasn't scared,

208
00:09:52,653 --> 00:09:54,092
I wouldn't be here.

209
00:09:56,772 --> 00:09:58,413
It's too profound to understand.

210
00:09:59,813 --> 00:10:00,813
You don't need to.

211
00:10:01,892 --> 00:10:03,173
As long as you're not scared.

212
00:10:04,132 --> 00:10:05,333
I'm not.

213
00:10:05,492 --> 00:10:06,853
When I was watching short videos,

214
00:10:06,933 --> 00:10:07,972
I saw a saying.

215
00:10:08,213 --> 00:10:09,213
It said,

216
00:10:09,533 --> 00:10:11,333
every ghost you fear

217
00:10:11,413 --> 00:10:12,772
is missed

218
00:10:12,852 --> 00:10:14,533
by someone.

219
00:10:15,933 --> 00:10:17,573
My sister is there with me.

220
00:10:18,132 --> 00:10:19,132
What am I scared?

221
00:10:20,053 --> 00:10:21,053
Makes sense.

222
00:10:23,492 --> 00:10:26,892
Then let's have a good sleep

223
00:10:27,132 --> 00:10:28,132
and have sweet dreams.

224
00:10:28,492 --> 00:10:29,213
Good night.

225
00:10:29,293 --> 00:10:30,293
Good night.

226
00:10:32,132 --> 00:10:33,132
I'll go to bed.

227
00:10:35,053 --> 00:10:36,053
Master, good night.

