♪I wish to meet you and embrace you♪

237
00:12:10,495 --> 00:12:14,136
♪A lifetime of destiny,
destined by heaven♪

238
00:12:14,616 --> 00:12:17,688
♪I need to give my all♪

239
00:12:17,976 --> 00:12:20,933
♪I wish to wander with you
