240
00:12:20,933 --> 00:12:22,493
If one day, I'm about to die,

241
00:12:22,573 --> 00:12:23,573
the one

242
00:12:23,933 --> 00:12:25,173
I want to be buried with

243
00:12:25,932 --> 00:12:29,400
♪A lifetime of happiness,
all entrusted to you♪

244
00:12:29,732 --> 00:12:30,732
