261
00:13:53,333 --> 00:13:54,333
Xiaomi, come on.

262
00:13:56,012 --> 00:13:56,732
Lili.

263
00:13:57,012 --> 00:13:58,052
Bring the ID Cards of

264
00:13:58,132 --> 00:13:58,854
Dami and Xiaomi.

265
00:13:58,934 --> 00:14:00,252
Qian Hao is taking them to play.

266
00:14:11,252 --> 00:14:12,333
Dad is here.

267
00:14:12,892 --> 00:14:13,772
Mom, Dad is here.

268
00:14:13,852 --> 00:14:14,852
Hurry up.

269
00:14:17,012 --> 00:14:18,132
