270
00:14:18,132 --> 00:14:19,892
yet stayed up watching TV

271
00:14:19,972 --> 00:14:20,972
and the tablet.

272
00:14:21,092 --> 00:14:22,533
Can't get up now, right?

273
00:14:22,933 --> 00:14:25,293
We're here. I can see my grandson now.

274
00:14:26,933 --> 00:14:28,372
Remember what I told you.

275
00:14:28,693 --> 00:14:29,652
You can't

276
00:14:29,732 --> 00:14:30,772
ignore Dami.

277
00:14:31,012 --> 00:14:32,892
If Dami is upset, she'll make a fuss.

278
00:14:32,972 --> 00:14:34,532
If it happens, Xu Kaixin won't

279
00:14:34,612 --> 00:14:35,813
let us see them again.

280
00:14:36,852 --> 00:14:38,453
I know. I am not that stupid.

281
00:14:38,533 --> 00:14:40,173
I can pretend it.

282
00:14:40,372 --> 00:14:41,372
As you wish.

283
00:14:41,573 --> 00:14:42,293
Yes, I know.

284
00:14:42,373 --> 00:14:43,813
